MuseScore_General.sf3
=====================

A high-quality (~39 MB) General MIDI soundfont in SF3 (OGG-compressed)
format. Full 128-instrument GM coverage + Roland GS extensions. Derived
from FluidR3 with selective improvements. Loaded via oxisynth's `sf3`
feature (lewton OGG decoder); compatible with both native and WASM targets.

